Formula:
FILTER (
    DISTINCT (
        SELECTCOLUMNS( FactSheet_TargetLines, 
                        "LineItem_X", FactSheet_TargetLines[LineItem_X],
                        "LineItem_Y", FactSheet_TargetLines[LineItem_Y],
                        "ID_X", FactSheet_TargetLines[ID_X],
                        "ID_Y", FactSheet_TargetLines[ID_Y])
    ),
    NOT ( ISBLANK ( [ID_X] ) )
)

Column: fx-Rate EoY (1 EUR = X local currency)
Naming: FinancialsYearly[fx-Rate EoY (1 EUR = X local currency)]
Financials[('fx-Rate EoY (1 EUR = X local currency)', 2016)]
Financials[('fx-Rate EoY (1 EUR = X local currency)', 2017)]
Financials[('fx-Rate EoY (1 EUR = X local currency)', 2018)]

Column: # of functioning screens with DS (RCPS etc.)
Naming: MPC_dealers[# of functioning screens with DS (RCPS etc.)]

Column: # of functioning screens with alternative solution to DS
Naming: MPC_dealers[# of functioning screens with alternative solution to DS]
MPC_dealers[# of new car showroom adapters]

Formula:
COUNTROWS(FILTER(MPC_dealers_offering,
                                        CONTAINS(ALLSELECTED('Competitor Comparison Categories'),
                                                'Competitor Comparison Categories'[Function],
                                                MPC_dealers_offering[value])))

SWITCH( MPC_dealers_offering[value],
                            "3S", 1,
                            "Sales + Service", 2,
                            "Sales only", 3,
                            "Service + Parts", 4,
                            "Service only", 5,
                            "Parts reseller", 6
                            )

var country = MAX(all_countries[Country Unique])
return CALCULATE( COUNTROWS(FactSheet_Charts), USERELATIONSHIP(FactSheet_Charts[Country], all_countries[Country Unique]) ) > 0
